</head>

<body
    class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark font-display text-gray-900 dark:text-white transition-colors duration-200 overflow-x-hidden">
    <div class="flex min-h-screen w-full flex-col">
        <header
            class="sticky top-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-between whitespace-nowrap border-b border-solid border-gray-200 dark:border-[#202f4b] bg-white dark:bg-background-dark px-10 py-4 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-8">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                    <div class="size-8 text-primary">
                        <svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 48 48" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path
                                d="M42.4379 44C42.4379 44 36.0744 33.9038 41.1692 24C46.8624 12.9336 42.2078 4 42.2078 4L7.01134 4C7.01134 4 11.6577 12.932 5.96912 23.9969C0.876273 33.9029 7.27094 44 7.27094 44L42.4379 44Z">
                            </path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight uppercase">Museo de Tanques</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center gap-9">
                    <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">Inicio</a>
                    <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">Exhibiciones</a>
                    <a class="text-sm font-medium text-primary font-bold border-b-2 border-primary" href="#">Explorador
                        Arquitectónico</a>
                    <a class="text-sm font-medium hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#">Eventos</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-1 justify-end gap-6 items-center">
                <button
                    class="bg-primary hover:bg-primary-dark text-white text-sm font-bold py-2.5 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-primary/30">
                    Boletos
                </button>
            </div>
        </header>
        <div class="relative w-full bg-[#0f1623] border-b border-gray-800">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 py-10">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-end gap-6">
                    <div>
                        <div
                            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-primary/20 border border-primary/30 w-fit backdrop-blur-sm mb-4">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">architecture</span>
                            <span class="text-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Infraestructura &amp;
                                Historia</span>
                        </div>
                        <h1
                            class="text-white text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black leading-tight tracking-tight mb-2 uppercase">
                            Explorador Histórico Arquitectónico
                        </h1>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-lg max-w-3xl">
                            Descubre la evolución estructural del antiguo arsenal convertido en museo. Desde sus
                            cimientos de 1910 hasta las expansiones modernas de alta tecnología.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex gap-3">
                        <button
                            class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#202f4b] hover:bg-[#2a3c5e] text-white text-sm font-medium py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors border border-gray-700">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">history_edu</span>
                            Archivo Histórico
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <main class="flex-grow container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-10 py-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8">
                <aside class="lg:col-span-3 space-y-6">
                    <section class="bg-background-card rounded-xl border border-gray-800 p-5 shadow-xl">
                        <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">timeline</span>
                            Historia del Edificio
                        </h3>
                        <div class="relative border-l-2 border-gray-700 ml-3 pl-6 space-y-8">
                            <div class="relative timeline-dot">
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary block mb-1">1910 - 1914</span>
                                <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase">Arsenal Real Original</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1 leading-relaxed">Construcción de los hangares de
                                    piedra y acero para reparación de artillería pesada.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="relative timeline-dot">
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary block mb-1">1942</span>
                                <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase">Expansión Bélica</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1 leading-relaxed">Se añade la Sala B con estructuras
                                    de hormigón reforzado para soportar blindajes pesados.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="relative timeline-dot">
                                <span class="text-xs font-bold text-primary block mb-1">2015</span>
                                <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase">Conversión a Museo</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1 leading-relaxed">Integración de sistemas de
                                    climatización y refuerzos sísmicos modernos.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    <section class="bg-background-card rounded-xl border border-gray-800 p-5 shadow-xl">
                        <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">construction</span>
                            Materiales y Diseño
                        </h3>
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div class="p-3 bg-background-dark rounded border border-gray-700">
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-text-secondary uppercase mb-2">Cimentación Reforzada
                                </h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Losas de 1.5m de espesor capaces de soportar el peso de
                                    tres Tiger II en una sola sección.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-3 bg-background-dark rounded border border-gray-700">
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-text-secondary uppercase mb-2">Viguería de Acero
                                    Riveteada</h4>
                                <h5 class="text-[10px] text-primary font-bold">Original 1912</h5>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Acero al carbono forjado, técnica de unión por
                                    calor manteniendo la integridad industrial.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-3 bg-background-dark rounded border border-gray-700">
                                <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-text-secondary uppercase mb-2">Sistema de Ventilación
                                    Hidráulica</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Diseño original para la extracción de gases pesados
                                    durante pruebas de motores en interiores.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                </aside>
                <div class="lg:col-span-6 flex flex-col gap-4">
                    <div
                        class="bg-background-card rounded-xl border border-gray-800 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden h-[650px] flex flex-col">
                        <div class="absolute top-4 left-4 z-20 flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <div
                                class="bg-[#131b2b]/95 backdrop-blur-md p-1 rounded-lg border border-gray-700 shadow-lg">
                                <button
                                    class="w-full flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 bg-primary text-white rounded text-xs font-bold mb-1 transition-all">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">layers</span>
                                    Diseño Actual
                                </button>
                                <button
                                    class="w-full flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 hover:bg-gray-800 text-gray-400 rounded text-xs font-bold transition-all">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">history</span>
                                    Plano Histórico (1942)
                                </button>
                                <button
                                    class="w-full flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 hover:bg-gray-800 text-gray-400 rounded text-xs font-bold transition-all">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">engineering</span>
                                    Red Eléctrica &amp; Refuerzos
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="absolute bottom-6 right-4 z-20 flex flex-col gap-2">
                            <button
                                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-background-dark border border-gray-700 text-white hover:border-primary transition-colors flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">add</span>
                            </button>
                            <button
                                class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-background-dark border border-gray-700 text-white hover:border-primary transition-colors flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">remove</span>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-full h-full relative blueprint-grid">
                            <svg class="w-full h-full absolute inset-0" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet"
                                viewBox="0 0 1000 800">
                                <path
                                    d="M650 50 H950 A20 20 0 0 1 970 70 V350 A20 20 0 0 1 950 370 H650 A20 20 0 0 1 630 350 V70 A20 20 0 0 1 650 50 Z"
                                    fill="#131b2b" stroke="#374151" stroke-dasharray="5,5" stroke-width="2"></path>
                                <path class="transition-colors hover:fill-[#1c2a44]" d="M50 400 H300 V700 H50 V400 Z"
                                    fill="#172236" stroke="#3359a3" stroke-width="2"></path>
                                <path class="transition-colors hover:fill-[#1c2a44]" d="M300 300 H700 V700 H300 V300 Z"
                                    fill="#172236" stroke="#3359a3" stroke-width="2"></path>
                                <path class="transition-colors hover:fill-[#1c2a44]" d="M700 400 H950 V700 H700 V400 Z"
                                    fill="#172236" stroke="#3359a3" stroke-width="2"></path>
                                <rect fill="#111827" height="100" stroke="#4b5563" stroke-width="2" width="120" x="180"
                                    y="300"></rect>
                                <rect fill="#111827" height="100" stroke="#4b5563" stroke-width="2" width="120" x="700"
                                    y="300"></rect>
                                <text fill="white" font-family="Public Sans" font-size="24" font-weight="900"
                                    opacity="0.1" text-anchor="middle" x="175" y="550">SALA A</text>
                                <text fill="white" font-family="Public Sans" font-size="48" font-weight="900"
                                    opacity="0.1" text-anchor="middle" x="500" y="500">SALA B</text>
                                <text fill="white" font-family="Public Sans" font-size="24" font-weight="900"
                                    opacity="0.1" text-anchor="middle" x="825" y="550">SALA C</text>
                            </svg>
                            <div class="absolute top-[38%] left-[50%] group cursor-pointer"
                                style="transform: translate(-50%, -50%);">
                                <div
                                    class="w-8 h-8 bg-primary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white ring-4 ring-primary/20 animate-pulse">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">home_repair_service</span>
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="absolute bottom-full left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 mb-4 w-56 p-3 bg-background-card border border-primary/50 rounded-lg opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity pointer-events-none shadow-2xl z-50">
                                    <p class="text-[10px] text-primary font-bold uppercase">Pilar de Carga Histórico</p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-white mt-1">Estructura original de 1912 expuesta que sostiene
                                        el techo abovedado de la Sala B.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="absolute top-[65%] left-[15%] group cursor-pointer"
                                style="transform: translate(-50%, -50%);">
                                <div
                                    class="w-6 h-6 bg-gray-700 border border-gray-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white hover:bg-primary transition-colors">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]">info</span>
                                </div>
                                <div
                                    class="absolute bottom-full left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 mb-4 w-48 p-2 bg-background-card border border-gray-700 rounded-lg opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity pointer-events-none shadow-xl z-50">
                                    <p class="text-xs text-white font-bold">Muro Perimetral de Piedra</p>
                                    <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 mt-1">Piedra caliza local de 60cm de espesor.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="bg-background-dark p-3 border-t border-gray-800 flex justify-between items-center text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-gray-500 tracking-widest">
                            <span>Modo Exploración: Activo</span>
                            <span>Referencia: Registro Nacional de Monumentos Ind. #882</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <aside class="lg:col-span-3 space-y-6">
                    <section class="bg-background-card rounded-xl border border-gray-800 p-5 shadow-xl">
                        <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">analytics</span>
                            Datos de Infraestructura
                        </h3>
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-gray-800 pb-2">
                                <span class="text-xs text-text-secondary font-medium">Superficie Total</span>
                                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase">12,500 m²</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-gray-800 pb-2">
                                <span class="text-xs text-text-secondary font-medium">Carga Máx. Piso</span>
                                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase">120 Ton/m²</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-gray-800 pb-2">
                                <span class="text-xs text-text-secondary font-medium">Altitud Techo</span>
                                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase">18.5 Metros</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-gray-800 pb-2">
                                <span class="text-xs text-text-secondary font-medium">Climatización</span>
                                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-primary uppercase">Estabilizada</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    <section class="bg-background-card rounded-xl border border-gray-800 overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
                        <div class="p-5 border-b border-gray-800 bg-[#131b2b]">
                            <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-lg flex items-center gap-2">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">visibility</span>
                                Vistas de Capas
                            </h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-2 space-y-1">
                            <label
                                class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#202f4b] cursor-pointer group transition-colors">
                                <input checked=""
                                    class="rounded border-gray-700 bg-background-dark text-primary focus:ring-primary h-4 w-4"
                                    type="checkbox" />
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-white">Zonas de Conservación</h4>
                                    <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400">Muestra áreas originales protegidas</p>
                                </div>
                            </label>
                            <label
                                class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#202f4b] cursor-pointer group transition-colors">
                                <input
                                    class="rounded border-gray-700 bg-background-dark text-primary focus:ring-primary h-4 w-4"
                                    type="checkbox" />
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-white">Sistemas de Ventilación</h4>
                                    <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400">Conductos industriales históricos</p>
                                </div>
                            </label>
                            <label
                                class="flex items-center gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#202f4b] cursor-pointer group transition-colors">
                                <input
                                    class="rounded border-gray-700 bg-background-dark text-primary focus:ring-primary h-4 w-4"
                                    type="checkbox" />
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-white">Rutas de Acceso Pesado</h4>
                                    <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400">Caminos diseñados para orugas</p>
                                </div>
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </section>
                    <div class="bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 rounded-xl p-5">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">help_outline</span>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="text-sm font-bold text-white">¿Sabías que?</h4>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
                                    El edificio fue originalmente un arsenal secreto. Sus gruesos muros se diseñaron
                                    para contener explosiones internas accidentales.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </aside>
            </div>
        </main>
        <footer class="border-t border-gray-800 bg-[#0b101b] pt-16 pb-8">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 lg:px-40">
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-12 mb-12">
                    <div class="max-w-xs">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-white mb-6">
                            <div class="size-6 text-primary">
                                <svg fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 48 48" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                    <path
                                        d="M42.4379 44C42.4379 44 36.0744 33.9038 41.1692 24C46.8624 12.9336 42.2078 4 42.2078 4L7.01134 4C7.01134 4 11.6577 12.932 5.96912 23.9969C0.876273 33.9029 7.27094 44 7.27094 44L42.4379 44Z">
                                    </path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <h2 class="text-lg font-bold">Museo de Tanques</h2>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Preservando la historia de la guerra blindada y honrando a
                            quienes sirvieron. Una institución educativa sin fines de lucro.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-12 md:gap-24">
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                            <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Visita</h4>
                            <a class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm" href="#">Horarios</a>
                            <a class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm" href="#">Mapa Arquitectónico</a>
                            <a class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm" href="#">Eventos</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                            <h4 class="text-white font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Investigación</h4>
                            <a class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm" href="#">Biblioteca</a>
                            <a class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm" href="#">Archivos Digitales</a>
                            <a class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white text-sm" href="#">Blog Histórico</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="border-t border-gray-800 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
                    <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">© 2024 Museo de Tanques. Patrimonio Histórico Industrial.</p>
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <a class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#"><span
                                class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">share</span></a>
                        <a class="text-gray-400 hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#"><span
                                class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">rss_feed</span></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>

</body>

</html>